{"tid":1329163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中火力】鄭若驊唔回應張超雄處理台殺人案建議","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:01:31.000Z","uid":27797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"696688c76d1b87ab05738893cdd1cf8f88e8a4ef","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552843/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%8F%B0%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552843%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyv7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=ebfbaa36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552843%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0&h=5575646b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552843/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%8F%B0%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%A1%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n再有民主派議員提出私人條例草案，希望解決台灣殺人案，正在北京訪問的律政司司長鄭若驊未有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊未有回應記者提問就離開，工黨張超雄是繼楊岳橋和尹兆堅後再提出私人草案，建議在《逃犯條例》和《刑事事宜相互法律協助條例》中，只排除內地和澳門，換言之移交安排適用於台灣，至於草案能否在立法會審議，仍有待秘書處和政府批准。<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：林鄭不同意楊岳橋提私人草案處理陳同佳案<br />\n<br />\n 公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋建議, 提出修訂《侵害人身罪》的私人條例草案, 用以處理台灣殺人案. 楊岳橋說, 接獲特首辦書面回覆, 行政長官林鄭月娥不同意, 將他提出的私人條例草案, 提交立法會審議.<br />\n        工黨張超雄亦提交私人草案, 建議修例將台灣包括在現時單次個案移交的安排內. 他指, 如果政府或建制派有任何不合理的修訂, 他就會撤回草案.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗再討論佢地係鬼定真心膠，總之集中火力屌鳩政府就無死</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66350db0faa77b898215e14158951106855f4fa","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"集中火力整文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9a25cf0a24d049fab3dbb011e791d4b21dbd50","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002ceb68748bca32d1c34f424e502185bbd8a332","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f24b810ae982645623ff4c1a28a8d50f8707f90","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bb64425d9dfdcf8abfec8b2e20a969c5b29bba","tid":1329163,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj